name: SOLCash
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
"SOLCash is a Solana (SOL) Rewards Token on the BSC (Binance Smart Chain). By simply holding, you will earn Solana (SOL) crypto currency. We use a unique reward system that gives reflections from each transaction to all holders.

The more SOLCash tokens you hold, the higher your $SOL reflections will be. SOLCash, The future of Reflections Tokens and passive income. Together, We will create the safest place on the BSC. "
